## Dashboard Design

### Sample Sales Dashboard Layout

```text
------------------------------------------------
|              Sales Dashboard                 |
------------------------------------------------
| Total Accounts | Opportunities | Revenue     |
------------------------------------------------
| Account List   | Recent Deals   | Activities |
------------------------------------------------
| Performance Charts and Analytics             |
------------------------------------------------
```

### Dashboard Components

#### Header Component

* Displays dashboard title.
* Shows user information.

#### Metrics Component

* Displays KPIs such as:

  * Total Accounts
  * Opportunities
  * Revenue

#### Account Component

* Displays account records.

#### Analytics Component

* Displays charts and performance metrics.

#### Activity Component

* Displays recent activities and updates.

### Benefits of Component-Based Design

* Reusability
* Easy maintenance
* Better scalability
* Faster development

