## Aura vs LWC

| Feature            | Aura Components                  | Lightning Web Components |
| ------------------ | -------------------------------- | ------------------------ |
| Framework Type     | Proprietary Salesforce Framework | Modern Web Standards     |
| Performance        | Good                             | Faster                   |
| JavaScript Support | Older Model                      | Modern ES6+              |
| Learning Curve     | Higher                           | Easier                   |
| Reusability        | Supported                        | Better Support           |
| Security           | Lightning Locker                 | Lightning Web Security   |
| Development Speed  | Moderate                         | Faster                   |
| Future Support     | Maintenance Mode                 | Recommended Framework    |

### Aura Example

```javascript
({
    handleClick : function(component, event, helper) {
        console.log('Aura Component');
    }
})
```

### LWC Example

```javascript
handleClick() {
    console.log('LWC Component');
}
```

### Why Salesforce Recommends LWC

* Better performance.
* Modern development practices.
* Easier maintenance.
* Improved security.
* Greater scalability.

